            </li>
            <li id="sat-athletes-tab">
                <h2>SAT Scores by Recruitment Status</h2>
                <div id="sat-athletes" class="graph"></div>
                <p>Respondents who identified themselves as recruited athletes reported an average SAT composite score more than 170 points lower than the average score reported by non-recruits.</p>
            </li>
